          }}>{`存储相关解决方案`}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <hr></hr>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "环境"
    }}>{`环境`}</h2>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`主机名`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`IP`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`role`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`操作系统`}</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`ceph-01`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`172.16.31.11`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`mon osd`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`CentOS7.8`}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`ceph-02`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`172.16.31.12`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`Osd`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`CentOS7.8`}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`ceph-03`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`172.16.31.13`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`osd`}</td>
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`CentOS7.8`}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>{`这个是官网的图 `}</p>
    <p><img parentName="p" {...{
        "src": "https://docs.ceph.com/en/mimic/_images/7c79c29c18fe63f3e72dc8af9524487f9068e450166d6cc79775bd37c8191317.png",
        "alt": "架构"
      }}></img></p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "步骤"
    }}>{`步骤`}</h2>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "安装ceph"
    }}>{`安装ceph`}</h3>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "主机名设置"
    }}>{`主机名设置`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`## ceph-01
hostnamectl set-hostname ceph-01
## ceph-02
hostnamectl set-hostname ceph-01
## ceph-03
hostnamectl set-hostname ceph-01
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "添加主机映射"
    }}>{`添加主机映射`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`cat << EOF >> /etc/hosts
172.16.31.11 ceph-01
172.16.31.12 ceph-02
172.16.31.13 ceph-03
EOF
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "关闭防火墙"
    }}>{`关闭防火墙`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`systemctl stop firewalld && systemctl stop firewalld
setenforce 0 && sed -i 's/^SELINUX=.*/SELINUX=disabled/' /etc/selinux/config 
iptables -F && iptables -X && iptables -Z
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "时间同步"
    }}>{`时间同步`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`yum install -y ntpdate
ntpdate
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "ssh无密钥访问"
    }}>{`ssh无密钥访问`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`## ceph-01节点执行
ssh-keygen 

ssh-copy-id ceph-01

ssh-copy-id ceph-02

ssh-copy-id ceph-03
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "准备repo"
    }}>{`准备repo`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`yum install epel-release -y
cat << EOF > /etc/yum.repos.d/ceph-deploy.repo
[ceph-noarch]
name=Ceph noarch packages
baseurl=https://download.ceph.com/rpm-luminous/el7/noarch
enabled=1
gpgcheck=1
type=rpm-md
gpgkey=https://download.ceph.com/keys/release.asc
EOF
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`国内用户可以用阿里的仓库`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/epel.repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/epel-7.repo
cat << EOF > /etc/yum.repos.d/ceph-deploy.repo
[ceph-noarch]
name=Ceph noarch packages
baseurl=https://mirrors.aliyun.com/ceph/rpm-luminous/el7/noarch/
enabled=1
gpgcheck=0
EOF
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "安装ceph-deploy软件包"
    }}>{`安装ceph-deploy软件包`}</h4>
    <p>{`ceph-1节点`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`yum install ceph-deploy yum-plugin-priorities python2-pip bash-completion -y
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`其他节点安装`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`yum install yum-plugin-priorities python2-pip bash-completion -y
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "创建一个ceph目录"
    }}>{`创建一个ceph目录`}</h4>
    <p>{`ceph-01节点`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`mkdir ceph-cluster
cd ceph-cluster
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "初始化ceph集群"
    }}>{`初始化ceph集群`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph-deploy new ceph-01
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "（可选）修改网络接口"
    }}>{`（可选）修改网络接口`}</h4>
    <p>{`如果有两个网卡，可以将管理和存储网分离`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`public_network = 172.16.0.0/16
cluster_network = 192.168.31.0/24
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "安装ceph软件包"
    }}>{`安装ceph软件包`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph-deploy install ceph-01 ceph-02 ceph-03
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`国内加速可以指定阿里云镜像地址，先在所有节点添加这个仓库`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`cat << EOF > /etc/yum.repos.d/ceph-luminous.repo
[ceph]
name=Ceph packages for x86_64
baseurl=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ceph/rpm-luminous/el7/x86_64
enabled=1
gpgcheck=0
EOF
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`然后执行`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph-deploy install ceph-01 ceph-02 ceph-03 --no-adjust-repos
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "创建mon"
    }}>{`创建mon`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph-deploy mon create-initial
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`执行完后会创建*.keyring 密钥环`}</p>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "复制配置和秘钥到对应的节点上"
    }}>{`复制配置和秘钥到对应的节点上`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph-deploy admin ceph-01 ceph-02 ceph-03 
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "部署mgr"
    }}>{`部署mgr`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph-deploy mgr create ceph-01
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`mgr是ceph-12.x版本(luminous)新增的组件`}</p>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "部署osd"
    }}>{`部署osd`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph-deploy osd create --data /dev/sdb ceph-01
ceph-deploy osd create --data /dev/sdb ceph-02
ceph-deploy osd create --data /dev/sdb ceph-03
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "检查集群状态"
    }}>{`检查集群状态`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph health
ceph -s
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "测试"
    }}>{`测试`}</h3>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "创建pool"
    }}>{`创建pool`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph osd pool create test 8 8
echo \`date\` > date.txt
rados put test-object-1 date.txt --pool=test
`}</code></pre>
    <h5 {...{
      "id": "上传到存储池中"
    }}>{`上传到存储池中`}</h5>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`echo \`date\` > date.txt
rados put test-object-1 date.txt --pool=test
`}</code></pre>
    <h5 {...{
      "id": "查看存储池和对象映射"
    }}>{`查看存储池和对象映射`}</h5>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`rados -p test ls
ceph osd map test test-object-1
`}</code></pre>
    <h5 {...{
      "id": "删除"
    }}>{`删除`}</h5>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`rados rm test-object-1 --pool=test
ceph osd pool rm test test --yes-i-really-really-mean-it
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`这里删不掉的话，需要添加这个配置`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`mon_allow_pool_delete = true
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`然后重启mon`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph-deploy --overwrite-conf admin ceph-01 ceph-02 ceph-03
systemctl restart ceph-mon@ceph-01.service
## 再执行删除
ceph osd pool rm test test --yes-i-really-really-mean-it
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "ceph-rbd对接kubernetes"
    }}>{`ceph rbd对接kubernetes`}</h3>
    <p>{`参考github连接：`}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://kubernetes.io/zh/docs/concepts/storage/storage-classes/#ceph-rbd"
      }}>{`https://kubernetes.io/zh/docs/concepts/storage/storage-classes/#ceph-rbd`}</a></p>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "创建pool-1"
    }}>{`创建pool`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph osd pool create kube-pool 64 64
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "导入admin-keyring"
    }}>{`导入admin keyring`}</h4>
    <p>{`获取admin keyring`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph auth get-key client.admin
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`将key换成上一步输出的结果`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`kubectl create secret generic ceph-secret  -n kube-system \\
  --type="kubernetes.io/rbd" \\
  --from-literal=key='AQDYuPZfdjykCxAAXApI8weHFiZdEPcoc8EaRA=='
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "创建-user-secret"
    }}>{`创建 user secret`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph auth add client.kube mon 'allow r' osd 'allow rwx pool=kube-pool'
ceph auth get-key client.kube
kubectl create secret generic ceph-secret-user -n kube-system  --from-literal=key='AQAH2vZfe8wWIhAA0w81hjSAoqmjayS5SmWuVQ=='  --type=kubernetes.io/rbd
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "创建storageclass"
    }}>{`创建StorageClass`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml"
      }}>{`apiVersion: storage.k8s.io/v1
kind: StorageClass
metadata:
  name: ceph-rbd
provisioner: kubernetes.io/rbd
parameters:
  monitors: 172.16.31.11:6789
  adminId: admin
  adminSecretName: ceph-secret
  adminSecretNamespace: kube-system
  pool: kube-pool
  userId: kube
  userSecretName: ceph-secret-user
  userSecretNamespace: kube-system
  fsType: ext4
  imageFormat: "2"
  imageFeatures: "layering"
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "worker节点安装ceph-common"
    }}>{`worker节点安装ceph-common`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`cat << EOF > /etc/yum.repos.d/ceph-luminous.repo
[ceph]
name=Ceph packages for x86_64
baseurl=http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ceph/rpm-luminous/el7/x86_64
enabled=1
gpgcheck=0
EOF
yum install -y ceph-common
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "创建pvc"
    }}>{`创建PVC`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolumeClaim
metadata:
  name: rbd-1
  namespace: default
spec:
  accessModes:
  - ReadWriteOnce
  resources:
    requests:
      storage: 1Gi
  storageClassName: ceph-rbd
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "创建deployment"
    }}>{`创建deployment`}</h4>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  labels:
    app: test-rbd
  name: test-rbd
  namespace: default
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: test-rbd
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: test-rbd
    spec:
      containers:
      - image: zerchin/network
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
        name: test-rbd
        volumeMounts:
        - mountPath: /data
          name: rbd
      volumes:
      - name: rbd
        persistentVolumeClaim:
          claimName: rbd-1
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "常见问题"
    }}>{`常见问题`}</h4>
    <h5 {...{
      "id": "问题1：rbd未加载报错"
    }}>{`问题1：rbd未加载报错`}</h5>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`MountVolume.WaitForAttach failed for volume "pvc-8d8a8ed9-bcdb-4de8-a725-9121fcb89c84" : rbd: map failed exit status 2, rbd output: libkmod: ERROR ../libkmod/libkmod.c:586 kmod_search_moddep: could not open moddep file '/lib/modules/4.4.247-1.el7.elrepo.x86_64/modules.dep.bin' modinfo: ERROR: Module alias rbd not found. modprobe: ERROR: ../libkmod/libkmod.c:586 kmod_search_moddep() could not open moddep file '/lib/modules/4.4.247-1.el7.elrepo.x86_64/modules.dep.bin' modprobe: FATAL: Module rbd not found in directory /lib/modules/4.4.247-1.el7.elrepo.x86_64 rbd: failed to load rbd kernel module (1) rbd: sysfs write failed In some cases useful info is found in syslog - try "dmesg | tail". rbd: map failed: (2) No such file or directory
`}</code></pre>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`原因`}</strong></p>
    <p>{`主要就是没有加载rbd模块，需要到所有的worker节点上加载rbd模块`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`解决`}</strong></p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`modprobe rbd
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`参考：`}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://forums.cnrancher.com/q_445.html"
      }}>{`https://forums.cnrancher.com/q_445.html`}</a></p>
    <h5 {...{
      "id": "问题2：挂载失败"
    }}>{`问题2：挂载失败`}</h5>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`MountVolume.WaitForAttach failed for volume "pvc-aa0d2e46-3df3-4c70-a318-ad95d4d0810a" : rbd: map failed exit status 110, rbd output: rbd: sysfs write failed In some cases useful info is found in syslog - try "dmesg | tail". rbd: map failed: (110) Connection timed out
`}</code></pre>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`解决`}</strong></p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph osd crush tunables hammer
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`参考：`}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://github.com/rancher/rancher/issues/13198#issuecomment-391920740"
      }}>{`https://github.com/rancher/rancher/issues/13198#issuecomment-391920740`}</a></p>
    <h5 {...{
      "id": "问题3：ceph-health_warn"
    }}>{`问题3：ceph HEALTH_WARN`}</h5>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`HEALTH_WARN application not enabled on 1 pool(s)
`}</code></pre>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`解决`}</strong></p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`ceph health detail
ceph osd pool application enable kube-pool rbd
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "部署cephfs文件系统"
    }}>{`部署cephfs文件系统`}</h3>
    <p>{`k8s默认没有cephfs的provisioner，所以需要手动部署一个provisioner去对接cephfs`}</p>
